MAR 4 – MAR 10, 2022A week dominated by Russia’s invasion of Ukraine and the horrors of war: Bodies in the streets; devastation at the children’s and maternity hospital in Mariupol; emotional farewells at train stations — and emotional reunions at border crossings. This photo gallery highlights some of the most compelling images made or published in the week by The Associated Press from Europe and Africa.Follow AP visual journalism:Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/apnewsAP Images on Twitter: http://twitter.com/AP_ImagesAP Images blog: http://apimagesblog.com